{"tid":1808590,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉］全部人入嚟 學識正確穿脫 口罩！","createTime":"2020-01-02T12:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T18:47:42.000Z","uid":162645,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"67de9c9c770e48efbf6797d70b2a7c11566e62d4","tid":1808590,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩點利益申報：<br />\n1. 我唔係 最標準，但求拋磚引玉<br />\n2. 戴得啱，同除得啱，同樣重要</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n入正題：<br />\n我諗基本戴口罩 大家都識，<br />\n我講兩個 竅門：（等大家再分享）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 唔好摺到 鐵線起角</span></strong><br />\n見好多人 戴之前會 先對摺口罩，<br />\n或者戴咗上去，用兩隻手指係個鼻位 夾一下<br />\n（見腦魔手指 位置）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFgpqz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFgpqz9.jpg&h=cf5f76a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之你個鼻唔係整容 整到起角，<br />\n就唔好整到個罩起角<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩 最重要係 要貼服！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 學識做 氣密測試</strong></span><br />\n（唔知係咪咁譯，air seal test)<br />\n簡單d講，就係要確保 所以出入既空氣，<br />\n都係 經口罩濾層出入，而非周圍 漏窿位<br />\n<br />\n呢個無論 外科口罩/n95同樣適用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇片（2:09）成條片都有用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/05wyH1-mLGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F05wyH1-mLGk&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=c3ce3e7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/05wyH1-mLGk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇片（2:09）成條片都有用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講住兩點先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除罩都係幾個準則</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 口罩 外面好污糟（用嚟阻隔細菌）<br />\n唔好掂到，從勾耳位除罩 <br />\n2. 除罩前後 請潔手（酒精/洗手）<br />\n3. 除罩小心橡根，切勿彈罩（會彈起細菌）<br />\n成件事等於自爆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹係拋磚引玉，<br />\n大家一定要好好保護自己，<br />\n萬一疫症爆發=人口篩選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>要身體健康，先可以光復香港！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f6e46391bba20d26fdc1873e5e43e95fb52bb4af","tid":1808590,"uid":317233,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">含撚啦泛民打手！<br />\n［最後通牒］警告泛民重回正軌 否則勇武將會全面退場攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808373</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ea8fa5ec93888767961c1049e7af3b8db53c3868","tid":1808590,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1d00052d2dc79e4505e076fd83eb3ecefa3825f5","tid":1808590,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"374a876e73ab2227dbea9dc327a929d7acb2d41d","tid":1808590,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8f604801985a9f342184fc8699d7a585a3738651","tid":1808590,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f9e05cb38caf84b5062ed992630e2aa2069535","tid":1808590,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:05:27.000Z","msg":"光復香港由港足做起<br />\n<br />\nWe are Hong Kong 🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\nOle ole ole<br />\n<br />\n本谷旨在有興趣睇港足港超或者有睇開的球迷入嚟討論波經。以老帶新，由資深球迷帶新手球迷入門，交換資訊，降低香港睇波門檻，等愈來愈多球迷入場撐港足，重建香港球巿<br />\n<br />\n光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=7