il_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為當年個仆街政府草菅人命，冇一早隔離大陸病人呀！<br />\n<br />\n咁你信唔信依家呢個政府會話俾你知真相？佢咁驚經濟差，仲會提你帶口罩？佢就係唔想人人帶口罩呀！<br />\n<br />\n你諗吓，假設你喺大陸中咗招，知道喺大陸好大機會死，而死咗官方都唔會認，咁你又知道香港醫生好犀利，咁你會點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾我就會先搭車去深圳，再落嚟香港，咁你個海關唔通每個大陸人都檢疫咩？<br />\n<br />\n同埋，你真係信大陸淨係武漢出事？唔會有人由武漢去其他省份？<br />\n<br />\n為求自保，出街帶口罩啦<br />\n<br />\n要一人行一步，防止社區爆發呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFrgXW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFrgXW1.png&h=6510022b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZaEUdw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZaEUdw.png&h=9c751baa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEvJBhZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEvJBhZ.png&h=95690e68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X59uwRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX59uwRt.png&h=40f9ad0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08TZUer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08TZUer.png&h=dc5f3de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOtZUes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOtZUes.png&h=eb37c162&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"891ff17064471a7ada289c1af2d5a3954b24caaa","tid":1808590,"uid":302944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:48:30.000Z","msg":"推 全城口罩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要教埋點分前後 見街好多人前後倒轉戴<img src=\"/